{"metadata":{"title":"Migrating to 1.14","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As the library prepares for Swift 6 we are in the process of updating the library’s APIs for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"sendability and isolation where appropriate, and doing so in a backwards compatible way. Prior","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to version 1.14 of the library the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","type":"reference"},{"text":" type has only ever been meant to be used on the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"main thread, but that contract was not enforced in any major way. If a store was interacted with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"on a background thread a runtime warning would be emitted, but the compiler had no knowledge of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the type’s isolation."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"That now changes in 1.14 where "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" is now officially ","type":"text"},{"code":"@MainActor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"-isolated. This has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"done in a way that should be 100% backwards compatible, and if you have problems please open a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"However, if you are using "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strict"}]},{"type":"text","text":" concurrency settings in your app, then there is one circumstance"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in which you may have a compilation error. If you are accessing the ","type":"text"},{"code":"store","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in a view method or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property in Xcode <16, then you may have to mark that property as ","type":"text"},{"code":"@MainActor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"code":[" struct FeatureView: View {","   let store: StoreOf<Feature>"," ","   var body: some View {","     \/\/ ...","   }"," ","+  @MainActor","   var title: some View {","     Text(store.name)","   }"," }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"diff"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Migr